40:06.337 --> 40:13.011 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Mount St. Helens
in Washington
state is one of the most
well-monitored volcanoes

40:13.044 --> 40:17.382 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
