brewing.

41:31.622 --> 41:36.761 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Two months before it blew, the
volcano was
venting huge amounts of steam
and there was

41:36.794 --> 41:42.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
