just a barren
landscape, gray and
pumice-colored.

42:27.311 --> 42:33.985 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: It killed every
living thing
in a 230-square-mile area. What
was left was

42:34.018 --> 42:42.660 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
